title: Dick Costolo

description:
Whitney catches us up on her new stand-up special aftermath, being a try-hard, and reveals the most embarrassing thing she's ever done in private. Then, former head of Twitter Dick Costolo is here talking about robots, surveillance, and consulting on HBO's SILICON VALLEY.
